translations: vi.（牛）发出哞哞声（moo 的过去式和过去分词）

sentences.sentence: Through the past 60 years, the friendly and cheerful bovine has "mooed" her way into the list of top ten ICONS of all time.
sentences.translation: 正解：过去的六十年来，这只友好欢快的牛一路“哞哞”叫着进入有史以来十大广告明星的行列。

sentences.sentence: Through the past 60 years, the friendly and cheerful bovine has come to embody all that is dairy and has " mooed " her way into the list of top 10 icons of all time according to Advertising Age.
sentences.translation: 过去60年中，这个和蔼可亲的奶牛形象已经成为体现奶制品一切特征的标志，并且一路“哞”声不断，进入了《广告时代》评出的有史以来十大顶尖广告形象的行列。
